pageContext.claim: “Former Democrat Senator Harry Reid just stated that Donald Trump is very smart, much more popular than people think, is underestimated, and will be hard to beat in the 2020 Election. Thank you Harry, I agree!”
pageContext.analysis: Reid actually said Trump had self-impeached with his conduct toward Ukraine. "You can't do what he did and go unpunished," he told "the Axe Files" podcast. Then, Reid said Trump was good at arguing.
